d.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb1586/697354584c684b12e1c830cd_Alside_Mezzo_Slider_Beauty2-2048x1365-p-500.avif 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb1586/697354584c684b12e1c830cd_Alside_Mezzo_Slider_Beauty2-2048x1365-p-800.avif 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb1586/697354584c684b12e1c830cd_Alside_Mezzo_Slider_Beauty2-2048x1365-p-1080.avif 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb1586/697354584c684b12e1c830cd_Alside_Mezzo_Slider_Beauty2-2048x1365.avif 2048w" class="wtypes-img"/><h4 class="wtypes-h4-3">Sliding Windows</h4><p class="collection-paragraph hidden-p"> Mezzo Dual Sliding Window sashes slide horizontally for easy opening and closing and lift out for convenient cleaning.</p></div></div><div role="listitem" class="collection-item-5 w-dyn-item"><div class="wtypes_grid-item-2 animated-scroll"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb1586/697354580f093e20b132664f_Alside_ECMezzo_DH_Beauty-2048x1358.avif" alt="" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb1586/697354580f093e20b132664f_Alside_ECMezzo_DH_Beauty-2048x1358-p-500.avif 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb1586/697354580f093e20b132664f_Alside_ECMezzo_DH_Beauty-2048x1358-p-800.avif 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb1586/697354580f093e20b132664f_Alside_ECMezzo_DH_Beauty-2048x1358-p-1080.avif 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb1586/697354580f093e20b132664f_Alside_ECMezzo_DH_Beauty-2048x1358.avif 2048w" class="wtypes-img"/><h4 class="wtypes-h4-3">Double Hung</h4><p class="collection-paragraph hidden-p">Both the beauty and smooth operation of Mezzo Double-Hung Windows will be a simple pleasure.</p></div></div><div role="listitem" class="collection-item-5 w-dyn-item"><div class="wtypes_grid-item-2 animated-scroll"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3