.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/694d39ac6ab8f7ccda788c35_vent-latch-coronado.jpg" alt="" class="glass-img-3 anlin-glass"/><p class="wtypes-h4-3">Ventilation Latch</p></div><div class="collection-paragraph">The built-in ventilation latch allows an opening space of few inches, while providing a semi-secure opening.</div></div><div class="wtypes_grid-item-2 glass-item no-cursor standard vertical"><div class="wtypes_inner vertical"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/694d3a44dd8aa5e90e71ee44_beveled-edges.jpg" alt="" class="glass-img-3 anlin-glass"/><p class="wtypes-h4-3">Beveled Edges</p></div><div class="collection-paragraph">Frames and sashes with matching beveled accents create a more polished and sleek look.</div></div><div class="wtypes_grid-item-2 glass-item no-cursor standard vertical"><div class="wtypes_inner vertical"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/694d3a81475782f51db6b0d7_double-hung-tilt-in.jpg" alt="" class="glass-img-3 anlin-glass"/><p class="wtypes-h4-3">Tilt-In Feature</p></div><div class="collection-paragraph">Double hung window features sashes that tilt in for easy cleaning of the outside glass and provides more air circulation when both sashes are open at the same time.</div></div><div class="wtypes_grid-item-2 glass-item no-cursor standard vertical"><div class="wtypes_inner vertical"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/694d3dd8ffd82c3757b832d5_frame-cutout-coronado.jpg" alt="" class="glass-img-3 anlin-glass"/><p class="wtypes-h4-3">Anlin <strong>X</strong>TRU</p></div><div class="collection-paragraph">Anlin’s proprietary Titanium Dioxide Infused Vinyl Extrusion is architecturally engineered for superior strength, durability and energy efficiency.</div></div><div class="wtypes_grid-item-2 glass-item no-cursor standard vertical"><div class="wtypes_inner vertical"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/694d3e27888933f40e8c1e16_rollers-balance.jpg" alt="" class="glass-img-3 anlin-glass"/><p class="wtypes-h4-3">Smooth Operation</p></div><div class="collection-paragraph">High-quality rollers and a constant-force stainless steel balance system make sliding and hung windows easy to operate.</div></div><div class="wtypes_grid-item-2 glass-item no-cursor standard vertical"><div class="wtypes_inner vertical"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/694d3e5f46e3e7cab7e3eef1_plus-easy-clean.jpg" alt="" class="glass-img-3 anlin-glass"/><p class="wtypes-h4-3">Easy Clean Glass</p></div><div class="collection-paragraph">PLUS Easy Clean Coating makes the outside windows easier to clean and helps them stay cleaner longer.</div></div><div class="wtypes_grid-item-2 glass-item no-cursor standard vertical"><div class="wtypes_inner vertical"><img sizes="100vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/694d3ee3ee4ac861cb1eaf67_anlin-armor-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/694d3ee3ee4ac861cb1eaf67_anlin-armor.jpg 600w" alt="" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/694d3ee3ee4ac861cb1eaf67_anlin-armor.jpg" loading="lazy" class="glass-img-3 anlin-glass"/><p class="wtypes-h4-3">AnlinArmor™</p></div><div class="collection-paragraph">AnlinArmor™ is an easy peel-off protective film on the interior and exterior glass that keeps your windows and doors in pristine condition throughout the manufacturing, delivery, and installation processes.</div></div><div class="wtypes_grid-item-2 glass-item no-cursor standard vertical"><div class="wtypes_inner vertical"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/694d3f58dff4925a95edb959_laminated-security-glass.jpg" alt="" class="glass-img-3 anlin-glass"/><p class="wtypes-h4-3">Anlin First Guard</p></div><div class="collection-paragraph">Optional laminated security glass provides greater protection from home invasions, adds critical response time and stops today’s smash and grab burglaries.</div></div><div class="wtypes_grid-item-2 glass-item no-cursor standard vertical"><div class="wtypes_inner vertical"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/694d3fa83dd7e2f3b0ff118f_sash-dead-bolt-coronado.jpg" alt="" class="glass-img-3 anlin-glass"/><p class="wtypes-h4-3">Sash Dead Bolt</p></div><div class="collection-paragraph">Optional solid ¼ stainless steel sash dead bolt provides added security.</div></div><div class="wtypes_grid-item-2 glass-item no-cursor standard vertical"><div class="wtypes_inner vertical"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/694d40437b6ae527780182ac_prevent-jimmying.jpg" alt="" class="glass-img-3 anlin-glass"/><p class="wtypes-h4-3">Continuous Interlock</p></div><div class="collection-paragraph">Continuous Interlock prevents “jimmying” the pull tight cam lock from the outside and passes the most stringent forced entry resistance test.</div></div></div></div><div class="about_content-wrapper w-condition-invisible"><div class="about_left"><p class="collection-p-big-2">The elegant narrowline construction ensures maximum daylight visibility while advanced technological reinforcements deliver dependable strength while minimizing energy transfer.</p><div class="left_grid-wrapper"><div class="left_grid-item"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" viewBox="0 0 25 28" fill="none" class="colleciton-icon"><path d="M12.01 23.7222C9.75767 23.155 7.8983 21.8628 6.43186 19.8454C4.96543 17.8281 4.23221 15.5879 4.23221 13.1249V7.19439L12.01 4.27772L19.7878 7.19439V13.1249C19.7878 15.5879 19.0545 17.8281 17.5881 19.8454C16.1217 21.8628 14.2623 23.155 12.01 23.7222ZM12.01 21.6805C13.6952 21.1458 15.0887 20.0763 16.1905 18.4722C17.2924 16.868 17.8433 15.0856 17.8433 13.1249V8.5312L12.