tab tabs-mob w-dropdown"><div data-dd="toggle" class="toggle-tab tabs-mob w-dropdown-toggle"><div class="tab-icon-wrapper"><div class="tab-icon-line"></div><div class="second-wrap"><div class="tab-icon-line second"></div></div></div><div class="toggle-text-tab-2">Warranty</div></div><nav data-dd="list" class="dropdown-list-4 w-dropdown-list"><div class="section_wrapper-2"><h2 class="h2-collection">Limited Double Lifetime Warranty</h2><h2 class="h2-collection w-condition-invisible">Limited Double Lifetime Warranty</h2><div class="about_content-wrapper"><div class="about_left warranty"><p class="collection-p-big-2">Anlin windows and doors are backed by the most inclusive limited lifetime warranty in the industry. Anlin will make warranty repairs free of charge for as long as you live in the home. Anlin’s limited lifetime warranty coverage is also transferable to one subsequent homeowner if you sell your home. That is two lifetimes of truly worry-free windows and doors.</p><div class="left_grid-wrapper one-column"><div class="left_grid-item"><div class="left_grid-content"><h4 class="wtypes-h4-2">What&#x27;s Covered:</h4><ul role="list"><li class="collection-paragraph">Parts</li><li class="collection-paragraph">Vinyl</li><li class="collection-paragraph">Insulated Glass Unit</li><li class="collection-paragraph">All Hardware (such as locks and latches)</li><li class="collection-paragraph">Insulated Accidental Glass Breakage</li><li class="collection-paragraph">Screen (only manufacturing defects)</li><li class="collection-paragraph">Labor</li><li class="collection-paragraph">Freight</li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class="about-right"><img sizes="100vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/694d27314626d0937bbd6820_anlin-warranty-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/694d27314626d0937bbd6820_anlin-warranty.jpg 800w" alt="" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/694d27314626d0937bbd6820_anlin-warranty.jpg" loading="lazy" class="image-32 right100"/></div></div><div class="about_content-wrapper w-condition-invisible"><div class="about_left"><p class="collection-p-big-2">The elegant narrowline construction ensures maximum daylight visibility while advanced technological reinforcements deliver dependable strength while minimizing energy transfer.</p><div class="left_grid-wrapper"><div class="left_grid-item"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" viewBox="0 0 25 28" fill="none" class="colleciton-icon"><path d="M12.01 23.7222C9.75767 23.155 7.8983 21.8628 6.43186 19.8454C4.96543 17.8281 4.23221 15.5879 4.23221 13.1249V7.19439L12.01 4.27772L19.7878 7.19439V13.1249C19.7878 15.5879 19.0545 17.8281 17.5881 19.8454C16.1217 21.8628 14.2623 23.155 12.01 23.7222ZM12.01 21.6805C13.6952 21.1458 15.0887 20.0763 16.1905 18.4722C17.2924 16.868 17.8433 15.0856 17.8433 13.1249V8.5312L12.01 6.34369L6.17665 8.5312V13.1249C6.17665 15.0856 6.72758 16.868 7.82943 18.4722C8.93128 20.0763 10.3248 21.1458 12.01 21.6805Z" fill="#1E73B9"></path></svg><div class="left_grid-content"><h4 class="wtypes-h4-2">Ultra Efficient Glass System</h4><p class="collection-paragraph">Further increase the energy efficiency of your Mezzo Windows with triple-pane glass protection.</p></div></div><div class="left_grid-item"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" viewBox="0 0 25 28" fill="none" class="colleciton-icon"><path d="M3.25999 22.75V14.9722H5.20444V19.4444L17.4544 7.19444H12.9822V5.25H20.76V13.0278H18.8155V8.55556L6.56555 20.8056H11.0378V22.75H3.25999Z" fill="#1E73B9"></path></svg><div class="left_grid-content"><h4 class="wtypes-h4-2">Lifetime Limited Warranty</h4><p class="collection-paragraph">Alside backs all Mezzo Windows with a Lifetime Limited Warranty, along with an optional glass breakage warranty.</p></div></div><div class="left_grid-item"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" viewBox="0 0 25 28" fill="none" class="colleciton-ic