77C16.0407 6.87437 14.2623 6.22217 12.2044 6.22217C10.0007 6.22217 8.12111 6.97564 6.56556 8.48258C5.01 9.98953 4.23223 11.8286 4.23223 13.9999C4.23223 16.155 4.98975 17.9901 6.50479 19.5052C8.01984 21.0202 9.85491 21.7777 12.01 21.7777Z" fill="#1E73B9"></path></svg><div class="left_grid-content"><h4 class="wtypes-h4-2">Cavity Foam Insulation</h4><p class="collection-paragraph">Mezzo Windows with enhanced cavity foam insulation are different than other windows. </p></div></div><div class="left_grid-item w-condition-invisible"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" viewBox="0 0 25 28" fill="none" class="colleciton-icon"><path d="M10.9892 17.4513L16.4822 11.9583L15.0968 10.5729L10.9892 14.6805L8.9475 12.6388L7.56208 14.0243L10.9892 17.4513ZM12.01 23.7222C9.75769 23.155 7.89831 21.8628 6.43188 19.8454C4.96544 17.8281 4.23222 15.5879 4.23222 13.1249V7.19439L12.01 4.27772L19.7878 7.19439V13.1249C19.7878 15.5879 19.0546 17.8281 17.5881 19.8454C16.1217 21.8628 14.2623 23.155 12.01 23.7222ZM12.01 21.6805C13.6952 21.1458 15.0887 20.0763 16.1906 18.4722C17.2924 16.868 17.8433 15.0856 17.8433 13.1249V8.5312L12.01 6.34369L6.17667 8.5312V13.1249C6.17667 15.0856 6.72759 16.868 7.82945 18.4722C8.9313 20.0763 10.3248 21.1458 12.01 21.6805Z" fill="#1E73B9"></path></svg><div class="left_grid-content"><h4 class="wtypes-h4-2 w-dyn-bind-empty"></h4><p class="collection-paragraph w-dyn-bind-empty"></p></div></div></div></div><div class="about-right"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb1586/696dce5216c84c4cf495e374_Alside_Mezzo_Slider_Beauty2-1024x683.jpeg" alt="" class="image-32 right100"/></div></div></div></nav></div></div></div></section></div></div></div><div class="section-120"></div><div class="f-section-large-3"><div class="f-container-regular-3"><div class="f-margin-bottom-64"><div class="w-layout-grid f-header-grid-asymmetrical"><div id="w-node-db7bfa11-9fa3-f74e-1b2d-e6e67af054c8-e8bdbfb8" class="f-max-width-large w-clea